      <div class="section">
        <h2>State Fire Claim Guides</h2>
        <p style="color: #dbeafe !important; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Click on any state to view specific deadlines, contact information, and regulatory requirements for fire insurance claims.</p>
        <div id="states" class="grid"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>National Claim Type Guides</h2>
        <p style="color: #dbeafe !important; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Comprehensive guides covering specific types of insurance claims with best practices and documentation requirements.</p>
        <div id="pillars" class="grid"></div>
